<p>marched back to Bazentin met Bas and had a yarn with him.<br/>Wednesday 28/3/17<br/>Inspection by Genl Birdwood who presented medals to the Battalion, marched to Scotts Redoubt Camp.<br/>Thursday 29/3/17<br/>Had a good sleep until mid-day, commenced to write report on operations.<br/>Friday 30/3/17<br/>Finished report on operations saw Bas had dinner with Wisdom also present Martin, Somerville &amp; Slane. Leave granted from Sunday.</p>
